# Production env for the recruiter dashboard on Vercel → app.interviehire.com
# Set these in the Vercel project's Environment Variables (Production scope).

# The hosted FastAPI backend on Railway (auth, jobs, applicants, reports).
# (railway.json holds the deploy config; env vars are set in the Railway dashboard.)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://interviehire-backend-production.up.railway.app/api

# The candidate interview room (the apps/web Vercel project) — used by the
# "Run test interview" launcher to open the room. Must be the domain where
# /interview actually returns 200 (the room's own Vercel deployment).
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENGINE_WEB_URL=https://interview.interviehire.com
